BRL is a language designed for server-side WWW-based applications,
particularly database applications. It is based on Scheme, which makes
the syntax extremely simple yet powerful. This implementation is a
Java Servlet using the Kawa Scheme compiler.

To download BRL via anonymous FTP, go to
ftp://download.sourceforge.net/pub/sourceforge/brl/

Faster downloads are likely via HTTP:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/brl/
